formation on available positions, job descriptions and benefits can be found on our website at: <a href=\"#\">www.stylemixthemes.com/vacancies</a>.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1453352470759{margin-bottom: 36px !important;}\"]\n<h4>H4  Lato Light, 24px</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][stm_separator border_color=\"green\" sep_line_width=\"60px\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1453353067171{margin-bottom: 70px !important;}\"]Throughout the year, students have continued to build a repertoire of performance pieces to include a variety of music and dance styles. Students continue to showcase their work during school assemblies and whole Secondary School events.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1453352654127{margin-bottom: 27px !important;}\"]\n<h5>H5  Lato Regular, 18px</h5>\n[/vc_column_text][stm_separator border_color=\"green\" css=\".vc_custom_1456478861745{margin-bottom: 31px !important;}\" sep_line_width=\"60px\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1453353661560{margin-bottom: 71px !important;}\"]Students from Secondary School MHS Band and the Secondary School Dance Team performed various songs and dance pieces during the \'Express Yourself\' Dance &amp; Music Event held at Secondary School on 9 December 2015.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1453352697607{margin-bottom: 28px !important;}\"]\n<h6>H6  Lato Regular, 14px</h6>\n[/vc_column_text][stm_separator border_color=\"green\" css=\".vc_custom_1456478866707{margin-bottom: 31px !important;}\" sep_line_width=\"60px\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1453353666776{margin-bottom: 71px !important;}\"]With schools in London, England, Secondary Schools\' curriculum includes the International Baccalaureate (IB) Programmes, and an American curriculum including Advanced Placement (AP) courses.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretc